DISPEL MAGIC

Useage      : cast 'dispel magic' <target>
Accumulative: No.
Duration    : Instantaneous.

  Dispel magic will wipe out all spells affecting a certain person or monster.
Dispel magic used on a sancted monster will result in a fight.

ex. If JoeBlow has poison and is cursed.
    cast 'dispel magic' JoeBlow

See Also: DETECT MAGIC
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
